        {
            "title": "〈臻鼎營運展望〉IC載板需求夯 旗下禮鼎科技也有上市掛牌規劃",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jjAKQFakvg7MTIyyYw5uGQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/609efe0688977341883b560f3516acee\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
