        {
            "title": "美股開市前，道指期貨跌逾200點！原油大升約6%，比特幣、美元齊升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周四，3月12日，美股開市前，美股指期貨全線調整，納指100期貨跌0.44%，道指30期貨跌260點，跌幅達0.55%，標普500期貨跌0.45%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"191\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NSEZG6o171K3ZnZA3meB0Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTE5MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/b9e3edc881d079732f773f216b787fb7\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金現報5179.04美元，白銀升1.25%至86.8美元。國際油價升約6%，倫敦布倫特原油期貨現升6.21%，報97.69美元；WTI原油期貨升5.68%，現報92.21美元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"664\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/js_whITLz2SGEV_usRkC2Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTExMzA-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/c1818641a4a24e1dfdfc550d2c42a120\" width=\"564\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元指數升0.16%，現報99.43。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"577\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MH0yZCWkRPrqXL_l7EQF1w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/86dd2ef72f4d53301b0e12a5fb9c2735\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">比特幣 (BitfinexUSD)升0.61%，逼近7萬美元大關。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-49513699-0855-3761-8696-4fb519d357b5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YvMaRq4I_i4QDTfBxrkgAA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/dffd00b81eda7be4353cd7b42295b4f6\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>3</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>月</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>精選股已上線，中東局勢擾動全球，</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>助您跑贏市場，</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"472\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4Ft3j2Y1BAXx4QqAkHhXrA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ3Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/f42d907d13c41ef90ddcfa4e6049c438\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><span><br/></span></p></blockquote></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E9%96%8B%E5%B8%82%E5%89%8D-%E9%81%93%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E8%B7%8C%E9%80%BE200%E9%BB%9E-%E5%8E%9F%E6%B2%B9%E5%A4%A7%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%846-%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3-%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E9%BD%8A%E5%8D%87-100753097.html",
